  creatureName: Nisse
  image: {fileID: 10905, guid: 0000000000000000f000000000000000, type: 0}
  description: "The Nisse is a grumpy and proud small creature that usually lives
    on a farm and helps the family who lives there. The Nisse mostly ignores people,
    but likes to be in control. Despite their small size, it is extremely strong,
    and loves to cause trouble. The Nisse can turn into animals. \r\nBe careful not
    to let the Nisse out of your sight, it might start some mischief to happen around
    you, maybe even involving you."
